            <p>Lishkee is currently in the process of creating their second full-length album, which promises to push their sound further while maintaining the intimate, experimental DIY aesthetic that defines their work. Following the success of their debut "Collections of Pink, Blue, &amp; All the Other Colors, Too," the upcoming album will showcase their continued growth as artists and their willingness to explore new sonic territories, from modular synthesis experiments to deeper collaborations with international artists.</p>

            <p>The band continues to balance studio work with live performances and multimedia collaborations, maintaining their connection to Brno's vibrant cultural scene while expanding their reach internationally through features like the Concrete Noir collaboration.</p>
          </div>
